snippet.title: Stellar Watch - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2058070?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=v2_trailer

Website: https://stellarwatch.gg
Twitter: https://twitter.com/whiteleaf_games

Stellar Watch is a tower defense game with space shooter elements. Deploy, upgrade, and research drones to protect the spaceship. Steer your ship to gain tactical advantages and outmaneuver your enemies.
